Current Price Range Minimum Increment $0 - $50 $1 $50 - $200 $5 $200 - $500 $10 $500 - $1,000 $25 $1,000+ $50 <p>Implementation: <pre><code>public BigDecimal getMinimumIncrement(BigDecimal currentPrice) {
